1. *Videli* smo sliku u galeriji. (We saw the picture in the gallery.)

2. Oni koji su *videli* sliku su se oduševili. (Those who saw the picture were delighted.)

3. Oni su *videli* da slika ima posebnu važnost. (They saw that the picture had a special importance.)

4. *Videli* smo da je to značilo mnogo za njih. (We saw that it meant a lot to them.)

5. *Videli* smo da je slika bila veoma lepa. (We saw that the picture was very beautiful.)

6. Oni koji su *videli* sliku su je zapamtili. (Those who saw the picture remembered it.)

7. *Videli* smo da je to značilo puno za njih. (We saw that it meant a lot to them.)